Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:10.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「月下獣・半人半虎」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Beast Beneath the Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Rashoumon Demonic Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「羅生門・天魔纏鎧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I don't want to have spent \Nall that money on nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これでは張った金額に遠く及ばんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三分を切った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.94,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:56.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan, if you'd prefer, I can \Nset you up with a life of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:50.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,殺しで生きる道を用意してやってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:02.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,けど　君の苦悩は君だけのものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,But your anguish isn't yours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成りたいものと向いているものが違う時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:07.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,What should one do, when what they \Nwant to be isn't what they're best at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人はどうすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:13.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Everyone fights, searching for the \Ncorrect way to live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:13.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生き方の正解を知りたくて　誰もが戦ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,What do they seek by fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何を求め戦う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,How ought they live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:20.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,No one can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:24.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,答えは誰も教えてくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我々にあるのは迷う権利だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:29.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,All we have is the right to waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,溝底を往く迷い犬達のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Like stray dogs that have hit rock bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:44.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:04.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:04.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:30.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若し　彼の云う通りなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.58,Stray Dogs - Italics,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,If he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.42,Stray Dogs - Italics,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,It is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　くだらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:41.05,Stray Dogs - Italics,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,The words of your past are fundamentally \Nunrelated to who you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:41.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故なら　苦しめる過去の言葉と貴様は　本質的に無関係だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:45.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若し今日この荷物を降ろして善いのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:46.85,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,If I may shed away my burden now, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Die, weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,砕け　人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,限界だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.13,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'm spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:09.22,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,If he stands back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:09.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若しこれで　奴が立ち上がったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ったぞ　ゼルダ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I won, Zelda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,待っていてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:29.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度…君に…幸福を…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:29.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'll bring you happiness once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　制御端末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Right, the control terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,愚者め
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:53.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I took it from him during the last attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:53.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の攻撃の刹那　奴から抜き取った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,は…早く止めないと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,We need to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:09.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I'd love to rip you to shreds right now but, \Nunfortunately, I've used up all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今すぐ八つ裂きにしてやりたいが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生憎力を使い果たした
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You'll have to make do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これで我慢しておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You're going to pay for \Nthis when we next meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:15.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　次会ったら覚えとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,下降？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Descending?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな　何もしてないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:34.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,寄越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,It isn't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,操作を受け付けぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが起こっている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ　こっちの操作も受け付けない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,It isn't responding here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,It's going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ落ちるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この声…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:57.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう時間がない　何か手を考えないとみんなが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,We need to do something, or everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,無駄じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,Someone has infiltrated from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:05.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,外部から何者かが侵入し　管制を奪っておる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,They've taken control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.14,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kyouka,0,0,0,,There's still a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ方法はある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この声…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらの状況は聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.97,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I heard about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「白鯨」の再浮上は無理でも　大質量で無理矢理叩き落とせば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,Even if the Moby Dick can't \Nbe stopped from falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:22.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,with enough force from above, it can be \Ndestroyed before it reaches the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,街に届く前に墜落させられる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I'll use this drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この無人機を使う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　凄いよ鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Kyouka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これでみんな助かる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,We can save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,落下傘の準備をお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Prepare the parachutes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君も早く脱出するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You need to escape now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,無理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私は虜囚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I'm captive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,My ankles are chained down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,足首が鎖で繋がれているから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I can't make it to the evacuation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出装置のある処まで行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…じゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:51.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことは諦めて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kyouka,0,0,0,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの駄目だ　軌道を変えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Change course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I didn't have a single \Nray of light until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで私には一片の光もなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:09.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,But today, I understood. I have choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　今日わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私にも選択肢はあると
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:17.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,If I sacrifice myself to save everyone \Nelse, I'll pass the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:17.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,命を犠牲にしてみんなを助ければ　きっと私は入社試験に合格できる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I can really become a \Nmember of the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に探偵社員になれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　何も惜しくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I would regret nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Akutagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん　聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:07.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして彼女が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Why her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Kyouka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,愚か者め
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:35.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,If she hadn't embraced the hope of living in \Nlight, she wouldn't have had to die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:35.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,光に生きる希望さえ抱かなければ　無駄に散らずに済んだものを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,This is how it ought to \Nhave been, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これでよかったのだよ　敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃんは自分に克ち　街を救った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:51.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan overcame herself \Nand saved the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社に相応しい高潔さでね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,With the high-mindedness \Nexpected of the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:58.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　彼女が死ななくちゃならない理由なんてどこにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,But there was no reason she had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,True, this is a merciless conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに厳しすぎる結末だね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:06.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　そうしなくてはならない理由があったのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,But there was a reason that \Nit had to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:11.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の異能力「人上人不造」は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:11.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0,0,0,,My ability, All Men Are Created Equal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:16.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0,0,0,,has an effect only on my subordinates...\NThat is, on members of the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:16.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の部下　つまり探偵社員にのみ発動する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:22.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その効果は異能の出力を調節し　制御を可能にする力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:22.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,The ability allows for control over the \Noutput of the abilities of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:29.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敦君が虎の異能力をある程度操れるようになったのも探偵社に入ったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:29.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,The reason you're able to control your tiger \Nabilities now is because you joined the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして鏡花ちゃんは入社試験に合格した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,And Kyouka-chan passed the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,衝突の直前にね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Right in the instant before the impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがどういうことかわかるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:49.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,白雪の刀で鎖を斬って脱出した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I used Demon Snow's katana to \Ncut the chain and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,You're hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ご…ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かったね　二人とも　秘密にして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Sorry I kept it from you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,If I hadn't, it wouldn't have \Nmade for a proper entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでないと　入社試験の審査にならなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最後は山？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.55,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0,0,0,,Do we end in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.51,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Rampo,0,0,0,,At sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,海だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.72,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Was this all planned from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして最初から全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,The enemy's been defeated, \Nand Kyouka-chan passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敵は打ち倒され　鏡花ちゃんは合格した
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I'm glad it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うまくいってよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,There's no one left to get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最早邪魔する者はない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日こそ僕の力を…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Please see my strength now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう限界に近いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You're at your limit now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ　ギルドの長を倒したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You just defeated the \NGuild's leader, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと　僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I am—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You've become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,強くなったね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ありゃりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いい眺めじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Nice view, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You protected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が守ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の街だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,It's your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:26.99,sign_16352_134_Episode_24_If_I_,Text,0,0,0,,Episode 24\NIf I May Shed Away \NMy Burden Now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,My city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の街　か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:34.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,横浜を巻き込んだ巨大異能力戦争も無事終結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,The massive gifted war caused so \Nmuch collateral damage in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,And it's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,But the government's work \Nis just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが政府の仕事はここからが本番ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Cleaning up after this huge mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この大騒ぎの後始末
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I won't be sleeping at home for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,家で寝られるのは何日後やら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:53.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Given that, we would very much appreciate \Nhaving your help, Mr. Herman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:51.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなわけで　我々としては貴方の助力を得られると大変助かるのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミスター・ハーマン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,I just want to watch the sea for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今は海を見ていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:04.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,With your information, we won't have to \Narrest Guild members who weren't part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:04.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴方の情報提供があれば　我々も無関係なギルド組員を逮捕せずに済みます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:10.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,Do you think that a mere grunt like \Nmyself would have such information?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:10.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂如き一介の構成員に　そのような知識があると思うか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:17.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,You were the leader of the Guild \Ntwo generations ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:17.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ貴方は　二代前のギルドの長ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:22.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若造は昔の話を持ち出したがって困る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:22.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Herman,0,0,0,,It pains me that you young'uns always \Ninsist on bringing up the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Please help us overcome \Nour sleep deprivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の睡眠不足解消にご協力ください
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I don't need to use this, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これは必要ありませんよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:54.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「白鯨」が沈んでる姿なんて　想像したこともなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I never imagined the Moby \NDick being underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,It was such a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いい場所だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.44,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,The Moby Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「白鯨」が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,The Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ギルドがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,The boss is missing in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,団長は生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:05.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,長を失ったギルドは混乱して内乱まで起こってるそうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I hear there are even insurgencies within \Nthe Guild, now that we don't have a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:10.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,Looks like it's time to lower \Nthe curtain on our adventures here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:10.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでの冒険活劇もエンドロールの時間ってことかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.72,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.43,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,But life isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも人生は終わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:15.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:20.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back home and \Nfinish working on my biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は本国に帰って　自伝執筆の続きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,What about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君達はどうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Louisa,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for Lord Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私はフランシス様を探します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Louisa,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,You're going back to your \Nfamily, right, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ジョンは家族の元に帰るんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.70,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,帰らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.72,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,I have to stop the insurgency in the Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ギルドの内乱を治める仕事がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,意外だね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,That's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I thought you hated the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は団長のことが嫌いだと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:44.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,金で人を操る人間は皆大嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I hate anyone who controls \Npeople with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:55.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,But he depended on his wealth to save \Nhis family, and this was the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:55.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　家族を救う為　富に頼り　その結果がこれだと思うと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま帰るというのもね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,I can't bring myself to just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Lovecraft,0,0,0,,The contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,契約…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Lovecraft,0,0,0,,is finally fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これでようやく完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,You made it, huh, Lovecraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,無事だったのかい　ラヴクラフト
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,What's going to become of you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君はこれからどうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Lovecraft,0,0,0,,I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,寝る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Mark,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は一体何者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何者でもいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.71,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.63,Stray Dogs - Default,John,0,0,0,,He's one of my few friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の数少ない友人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:38.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,せーの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.83,Stray Dogs - Default,A,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:02.33,Stray Dogs - Default,A,0,0,0,,Congratulations on joining \Nthe Agency, Kyouka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:01.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん　入社おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.84,Stray Dogs - Default,A,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,怪我はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,How are your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう大丈夫です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:38.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今回お前達の行動で　街は壊滅を免れた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:38.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Your actions have saved the \Ncity from destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,社の先輩として　一言云うべきだろうと思ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,I thought I should say something, \Nas your senior here at the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:50.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも探偵社という集団組織において　単独作戦は例外なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:50.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,First of all, solo operations are an \Nexception at group organizations such as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:58.31,sign_26473_193_Blah__blah__blah,Text,0,0,0,,Blah, blah, blah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,I won't tell you not to apply the experience \Nyou gained from this in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の成功を以降に活かすなとは云わんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,but don't dare neglect the \NAgency's prime activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,社の基本動作は疎かにするな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Likewise for Kyouka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花も同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Be mindful of the fact that you are \Na member of the Detective Agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社員として自覚を持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,決して恥ずべき行いを後に残さぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,and act in a way that none \Nwould be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,肝に銘じて行動しろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:01.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,No kidding, Kunikida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.07,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,まったくだねぇ　国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どいつもこいつも　酒付き合いが悪くてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:04.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,You're all such buzzkills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと付き合いな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,Drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather not drink much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　俺もそれ程には…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:12.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ　一言云いたかったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,Isn't there something you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,You did well, the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,二人とも　よくやったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　朝まで飲むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,All right, let's drink all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.28,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,そ…それはちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Please, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you can't drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずべき行いを後に残すな…か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.67,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Act in a way that none \Nwould be ashamed of, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,春野さん　ナオミさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Haruno-san, Naomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,すみませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I did some awful things to \Nyou thanks to Q's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｑの異能力を受けて　お二人に非道い事を…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:43.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の危うさをわかっていれば　あんなことには…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,It would never have happened if \NI'd known how unstable I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.78,Stray Dogs - Default,A,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時の
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:54.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に　すみませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:58.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun, that wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここじゃ　あの程度のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一々引きずっていられませんわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0,0,0,,We can't keep holding \Non to stuff like that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:12.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本当にどうかしてました　お二人にあんな非道いことをするなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:12.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,There was something seriously wrong with \Nme, to have done what I did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.39,TEXT-JP-ja,1,15,15,0,,敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0,0,0,,I've never heard about this until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:18.98,TEXT-JP-ja,1,15,15,0,,今の話　初耳なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.40,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}ねぇ　敦君　どういうことなの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.36,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}お…落ち着いてください　谷崎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.35,Stray Dogs - Top,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Please, stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.70,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,乱歩君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:28.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Poe,0,0,0,,Rampo-kun, I brought the new piece that \Nyou inquired about over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.14,Stray Dogs - Top,Kunikida,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.01,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}ボクはどうにも落ち着けない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.51,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,電話で頼まれた新作を持ってきたのであるが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:27.41,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}あたし　もうお嫁にいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.94,Stray Dogs - Top,Naomi,0,0,0,,I'm damaged goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.91,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,2,15,15,0,,{\an7}国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.92,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}ナ　ナオミさん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.82,Stray Dogs - Top,Yosano,0,0,0,,Kunikida!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.07,Stray Dogs - Top,Atsushi,0,0,0,,N-Naomi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0,0,0,,Yosano-sensei, I think you've \Nhad too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.86,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,2,15,15,0,,{\an7}与謝野女医　飲み過ぎでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.41,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,ああ　君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.86,Stray Dogs - Top,Rampo,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.68,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,よく来たね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:37.19,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,こんな場に吾輩を呼んでよいのであるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.20,Stray Dogs - Top,Tanizaki,0,0,0,,A-Atsushi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Poe,0,0,0,,Do I really belong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.61,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,乱歩さん　社長がお呼びです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.53,Stray Dogs - Top,Kenji,0,0,0,,Rampo-san, the boss wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.25,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,吾輩は敵組織の…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Poe,0,0,0,,I'm from an enemy organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.36,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,すぐ戻るから　そこにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.66,Stray Dogs - Top,Atsushi,0,0,0,,K-Kyouka-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.80,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.72,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,乱歩君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Poe,0,0,0,,Rampo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.83,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,2,15,15,0,,{\an7}飲む　国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.46,Stray Dogs - Top,Yosano,0,0,0,,Kunikida!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0,0,0,,That was an impressive operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.08,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,見事な策だった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.96,Stray Dogs - Top,Kyouka,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kyouka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.88,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}ちょっと待って鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.42,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.25,Stray Dogs - Top,Kyouka,0,0,0,,Don't make excuses, it's unmanly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0,0,0,,The Agency would be nothing without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.31,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}言い訳は男らしくない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.89,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,矢張り乱歩がいてこその探偵社だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.00,Stray Dogs - Top,Atsushi,0,0,0,,What did you tell her, Tanizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.83,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}何云ったんですか　谷崎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.10,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,まあねまあね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:54.71,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}キミの破廉恥なあんなことやこんなことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.21,Stray Dogs - Top,Tanizaki,0,0,0,,All the naughty things you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.81,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,流石が乱歩さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.57,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,2,15,15,0,,{\an7}いい飲みっぷりじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.15,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,まあねまあね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:55.88,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,1,15,15,0,,{\an9}ナオミさん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:58.40,TEXT-JP-ja,3,15,15,0,,なんかとても楽しそうであるな　カール
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Poe,0,0,0,,They seem to be having fun, huh, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.40,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,2,15,15,0,,{\an7}国木田　飲みます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.40,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,4,15,15,0,,まあねまあね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.31,sign_29590_272_He_likes_being__,Text,0,0,0,,He likes being\Nleft out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,It's a '64 Romane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ロマネの六十四年ものです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,May I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,よいのかえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Isn't it your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,秘蔵の品じゃろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:19.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,Is there a better day than today to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:19.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日よりも　こいつを開けるのに相応しい日があるってのかい　姉さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,To victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃ美味い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:33.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,Boss, how shall we punish Akutagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領　芥川の処罰はどうします
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Punish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,処罰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,He was instrumental in our success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は今回の成功の功労者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Akutagawa-kun has always been this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川君は昔からそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:46.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,He runs off by himself, he causes \Ndestruction and, in the end, he contributes the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:46.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,独走し　破壊し　結果　最大の貢献をする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼なりの嗅覚だろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,He has a strong nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成功している限り処罰はない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,So long as he continues to succeed, \Nthere will be no punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ところで紅葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:59.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Say, Kouyou-kun, why did you not try to \Nescape when you were captured by the Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:59.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社に囚われた時　何故逃げなかったのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,It ought to have been easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君なら脱出は容易だったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故かのう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,茶が美味かったからかのう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Perhaps because the tea was so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:12.46,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0,0,0,,Sister, let's make a deal, as two grown-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,姉さん　大人の取引をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.09,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0,0,0,,I have a plan for saving Kyouka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃんを助ける計画がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.34,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Kouyou,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:23.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成功すれば　彼女の命と夢を同時に守れる唯一の方法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:23.55,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0,0,0,,If we succeed, it'll be the only way to \Nprotect both her life and her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:30.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Dazai saw how it would all play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:30.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰は今回の結末まで凡て見えておった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,What a terrifying man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしい男じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,Pfft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Kouyou-kun, you are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,紅葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は強い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:44.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Now that your beloved Kyouka-kun is gone, it \Nwould be difficult for me to chase you down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:41.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が大切にしていた鏡花君がいなくなった今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:46.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若し君がポートマフィアを去る気なら　追うのは難しいだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,should you decide to leave \Nthe Port Mafia now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,無論じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:54.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが生憎と　頼りない首領が組織を立て直す手伝いがあるでのう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:54.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Sadly, I must help a clumsy leader \Nwith reestablishing the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,嬉しい話だが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:01.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I'm grateful, but I deal only \Nwith those under twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の守備範囲は１２歳以下だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ　口を縫い合わすぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0,0,0,,I'll sew your lips shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰　次は絶対死なす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuya,0,0,0,,You're so dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…あの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.36,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.90,Stray Dogs - Default,A,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.49,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.33,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,可愛い　こっち向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Dazai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば太宰さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:36.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,変な絵だね　これなら私にも描けそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,What a weird painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I bet even I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Hirotsu-san, thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,広津さん　例の件助かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Did I do enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの程度でよかったのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:51.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,All I did was leak the Moby Dick \Ninfiltration route to Higuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:51.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私は白鯨潜入を樋口君に漏らしただけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:54.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,If she knows, she will tell Akutagawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女が知れば　芥川君に伝わる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:59.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川君が知れば　必ず単身で乗り込んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:59.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,If Akutagawa-kun knows, he \Nwill come in by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,It was as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,予想通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:07.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうまでして芥川君と虎の少年を引き合わせた理由は何かね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Why did you go through all that trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:07.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,to bring Akutagawa-kun \Ntogether with the tiger boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I wanted to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かめたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:15.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,For the {\i1}real{\i0} disaster that's about to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:15.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,間もなく来る本当の災厄に備える為にね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,He's already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は既に動いている筈だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,So the destruction of the \NMoby Dick was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「白鯨」の墜落には失敗しましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:28.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　ほぼ計画通りです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:27.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,Still, just about everything \Nis according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:33.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,We succeeded in creating strife within the \NGuild and recruiting talented gifteds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:33.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ギルドに内乱を誘発させ　有能な異能力者の勧誘にも成功しましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Nathaniel,0,0,0,,I'm only helping for the time being \Nto fulfill my end of the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私は意識不明のマーガレットを治すという条件で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:41.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Nathaniel,0,0,0,,and have Margaret brought \Nback to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:41.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一時的に手を貸しているだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,That's fine by me, Pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:51.99,Typewriter Text Sign,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(529,54)}Fyodor D.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:51.99,sign_34953_329_Ability___Crime_,Text,0,0,0,,Ability:\N Crime and \NPunishment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,結構です　牧師殿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:51.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Nathaniel,0,0,0,,Let us paint the land with the \Nblood of the guilty together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:51.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,共にこの地を　罪深き者の血で染めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:55.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,よりよき世界の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Nathaniel,0,0,0,,For a better world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:03.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,We won't be able to avoid going to war \Nwith that demon I've fought in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,嘗て私が会ったあの魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:03.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,奴との戦いは避けられないだろうからね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:08.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川君は単独でも十分破壊的だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:08.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Akutagawa-kun is formidable enough by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:12.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,but his abilities are most \Nvaluable in a supporting role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:12.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,15,350,0,,本来は後衛で真価を発揮する異能力者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,In complementing a forward \Nattacker such as Atsushi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:16.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敦君のような速度と根性骨を持つ前衛を補助すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:18.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,with his speed and toughness, \Nhe could be a powerful ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:18.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,凄まじい戦力になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:25.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,We'll need to be more powerful than before \Nin order to fight with that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:25.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの魔人と戦う為には　これまで以上に強い力が要る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Something more powerful than \Nthe former Double Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:29.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,嘗ての「双黒」を超える新しい力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,That's those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがあの二人です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Dazai-kun, why do you \Nvalue Yokohama so dearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:41.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,15,200,0,,君がそれほどまでにこの横浜を大切に思っているのは何故かね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:44.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,My friend said me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:44.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,古い友人に云われたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:49.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,"You might as well side with \Nthe people who save others."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせなら　人を救う側になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:53.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,"That's at least a little more beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのほうが幾分か素敵だ　とね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:58.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Teni Muhou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:58.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「天衣無縫」か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:06.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕達が守った街
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:06.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,The city we protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Worthless nonsense.
